The paper focuses on learning-based approaches for semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task, making cs.CV the most likely sub-category. The paper also introduces a new active learning strategy based on deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning, making cs.LG and cs.AI likely sub-categories as well. The paper also involves decision-making based on predictions and uncertainties, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
